        229.08648681640625,
        102.27616882324219
      ],
      "text": "Soil Moisture Observation  \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 5,
      "page": 10,
      "bbox": [
        96.12000274658203,
        121.23078918457031,
        553.6400756835938,
        178.47618103027344
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nSoil moisture during 06 June \u2013 12 June 2026 is similar to the average of the past 10 years in \nmajor parts of Rajasthan, Gujarat, Madhya Pradesh, Maharashtra, Northern and Central \nKarnataka, Punjab, Bihar, Jharkhand, Uttarakhand, Uttar Pradesh H.P., Tamil Nadu, Kerala, \nWest Bengal and J & K. \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 6,
      "page": 10,
      "bbox": [
        96.12000274658203,
        180.87078857421875,
        553.7322387695312,
        208.47618103027344
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nSoil moisture is better than the average of the past 10 years in parts of Ladakh, pockets of \nRajasthan and Northern West Bengal. \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
    {
      "block_index": 7,
      "page": 10,
      "bbox": [
        96.12000274658203,
        210.87078857421875,
        553.7660522460938,
        253.2361602783203
      ],
      "text": "\uf0b7 \nIt was lower than average of past 10 years in pockets of Odisha, Chhattisgarh, pockets of \nHaryana, Southern Karnataka, Maharashtra, Andhra Pradesh and in the Northeastern parts of \nCountry. \n",
      "type": "text",
      "source_type": "pdfblock"
    },
